# Approach
***Remember, You can't take maximum frequent element as problem explicitly says that a substring is needed.
Substring is nothing but a continuous collection of strings.***

1) Use a greedy approach to make every partition.
2) Whenever you find a element that already exist in a 1D ArrayList ```arr``` then add ```arr``` to ```main```(2D ArrayList).
if not then add elements to ```arr```.
