**Recursive** :

```
class Solution {
    public int partitionString(String s) {   
        return partitionStringRecursion(s, 0, new HashSet<>());
    }

    private int partitionStringRecursion(String s, int index, Set<Character> chars) {
        // Base Condition
        if (index == s.length()) {
            return 1;
        }

        int charCanBeAdded = 0, charCannotBeAdded = 0;
        if (chars.add(s.charAt(index))) {
            charCanBeAdded = partitionStringRecursion(s, index+1, chars);
        } else {
            charCannotBeAdded = 1 + partitionStringRecursion(s, index, new HashSet<>());
        }
        return Math.max(charCanBeAdded, charCannotBeAdded);
    }
}
```

